      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHRONIC CHARLIE (6) caught the eye on debut when was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 2.25 lengths second (23.19) over 400m at this track. Exciting type and looks a top chance to break through. REBORN HARMONY (1) was below expectations on debut finishing fourth (24.14) at this track. Meets a moderate line up and should do much better. CYCLONE BEAST (2) turned spotting a big start finishing eighth (23.54) last time in a Maiden at Maitland. Some good form is emerging from her last run. One of the main contenders. LITTLE MIMI (7) can sneak into the finish.",
